Furthermore, retracting your original post seems an example of cowardice; your afraid of what people said, and so removing it before any more flaws are seen.<br>
<br>
But, what it all boils down to is this: You need to learn how to have fun with what you have. If its not fun, change classes, be bored, or adapt and find a way to have fun. Also, get a sense of humor...your skill at detecting sarcasm and humor is at 1/255. You seriously need to train that skill =)<br>
<br>
Peace out! <p>Dexanth Dragonborne <BR>

